            <polygon points="50,8 78,32 50,42 22,32" fill="url(#grad1)" opacity="0.3"/>
            <path d="M50 8 L78 32 L50 42 L22 32 Z" stroke="#dea882" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/>
            <polygon points="22,32 50,112 50,42" fill="url(#grad1)" opacity="0.2"/>
            <polygon points="78,32 50,112 50,42" fill="url(#grad1)" opacity="0.15"/>
            <path d="M22 32 L50 112 L78 32" stroke="#dea882" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/>
            <path d="M50 8 L38 32 M50 8 L62 32" stroke="#dea882" stroke-width="0.75" opacity="0.6"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="story-visual__sparkles"><div class="sparkle"></div><div class="sparkle"></div><div class="sparkle"></div><div class="sparkle"></div><div class="sparkle"></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="story-split__content">
        <span class="story-label">The beginning</span>
        <h2 class="story-heading">{{ section.settings.origin_title | default: 'A New York workshop since 1962' }}</h2>
        <div class="story-text">
          {% if section.settings.origin_text != blank %}{{ section.settings.origin_text }}{% else %}<p>The Milman atelier opened on West 47th Street in 1962. Three generations have worked at the bench since: cutters, setters, designers — the same family, the same standard.</p><p>What changed is the world. Lab-grown stones now arrive in our atelier with the same grading authority and a clearer line of provenance than the natural ones we set thirty years ago. The hand that finishes the piece is the same.</p>{% endif %}
        </div>
        <a href="/pages/our-story" class="story-text-link" style="display: inline-block; margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 0.78rem; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent-gold); text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--accent-gold); padding-bottom: 2px; transition: opacity 0.3s ease;">Read the heritage</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Three Pillars -->
  <section class="story-section story-section--dark story-section--pillars">
    <div class="story-container">
