        <div class="story-pillar">
          <svg class="story-pillar__icon" viewBox="0 0 60 60" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M30 5 L55 25 L55 45 L30 55 L5 45 L5 25 Z"/><circle cx="30" cy="30" r="8"/></svg>
          <div class="story-pillar__number">01</div>
          <h3 class="story-pillar__title">{{ section.settings.pillar_1_title | default: 'Every stone, hand-selected' }}</h3>
          <p class="story-pillar__text">{{ section.settings.pillar_1_text | default: 'Every centre stone is reviewed by hand in the atelier and graded independently by IGI or GIA. We accept the stones we would set in our own family’s pieces.' }}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="story-pillar">
          <svg class="story-pillar__icon" viewBox="0 0 60 60" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><circle cx="30" cy="30" r="25"/><path d="M30 5 L35 30 L30 55 L25 30 Z"/></svg>
          <div class="story-pillar__number">02</div>
          <h3 class="story-pillar__title">{{ section.settings.pillar_2_title | default: 'Provenance on paper' }}</h3>
          <p class="story-pillar__text">{{ section.settings.pillar_2_text | default: 'Every piece arrives with its certificate. The path from seed crystal to finished setting is documented — and the documentation comes home with you.' }}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="story-pillar">
          <svg class="story-pillar__icon" viewBox="0 0 60 60" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M30 5 L45 25 L30 55 L15 25 Z"/><circle cx="30" cy="25" r="12"/></svg>
          <div class="story-pillar__number">03</div>
          <h3 class="story-pillar__title">{{ section.settings.pillar_3_title | default: 'Made by hand, in New York' }}</h3>
          <p class="story-pillar__text">{{ section.settings.pillar_3_text | default: 'Designed and finished by master setters in our New York atelier. Three generations of hand. No work contracted abroad.' }}</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem;">
        <a href="/collections" class="btn btn--gold btn--lg">Explore the collection</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Craft -->
  <section class="story-section story-section--split story-section--reverse">
    <div class="story-split">
      <div class="story-split__content">
        <span class="story-label">The work</span>
        <h2 class="story-heading">{{ section.settings.craft_title | default: 'The atelier' }}</h2>
        <div class="story-text">
          {% if section.settings.craft_text != blank %}{{ section.settings.craft_text }}{% else %}<p>Each piece is finished at the bench in our New York atelier — by master setters from the Milman family workshop. Three generations of hand. Nothing contracted out, nothing assembled abroad.</p><p>We do not mass-produce. Each piece is sized, set, and polished individually before it leaves the atelier.</p>{% endif %}
